    "en": {
      "title": "I know how the current president is",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Former Presidential Member of Parliament Maithripala Sirisena says that he has governed with the current President for five years and he knows him very well.",
        "The former president said that it is not appropriate to see politicians as black or white based on the current situation in the country and everyone should remove party colors from their heads at this time.",
        "The former president mentioned this when journalists asked about the all-party government."
      ],
